data.title: A Main to Sands Door Razorvine
data.description: Prevent Defenders from taking aggressive peeks and fights towards the Sands Door early into the round with this lineup.

data.title: B Site Razorvine And Arc Rose Execute
data.description: Use this simple, but effective combination of utility to execute the B Site. Defenders playing behind the boxes will be forced to fight or take damage, as well as getting flashed if they are looking at Attackers scaling up.
